Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Off the hook?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b0440ft9
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 11 Oct 1987
A question of intelligence - the definition which just might prove that providing assistance to the Contras broke no US law. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less